{{Infobox television | show_name = Eye to Eye | image = Eye to Eye title card.png | caption = Title card of ''Eye To Eye'' | image_size = 260px | rating = | creator = | presenter = Francine Lacqua | executive_producer = | country = United Kingdom | language = English | network = [[Bloomberg Television]] | picture_format = | location = [[London Eye]], U.K. | camera = [[Multi-camera]] | distributor = | num_series= | company = | runtime = 30 minutes <small>({{tooltip|inc.|including}} adverts)</small> | first_aired = {{start date|2011|3|28}} | last_aired = present | num_episodes = | website = https://www.bloomberg.com/tv/shows/eye-to-eye/ }}
'''''Eye to Eye''''' is a business-themed television interview program hosted by [[Francine Lacqua]], which airs in selected regions on [[Bloomberg Television]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.kettlemag.com/article/interview-bloomberg-television-anchor-and-editor-large-francine-lacqua|title=Interview with Bloomberg Television Anchor and Editor-at-Large, Francine Lacqua|date=31 July 2015|work=Kettle Mag|first=Rebecca|last=Parker|accessdate=15 August 2015|archivedate=15 August 2015|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150815074522/http://www.kettlemag.com/article/interview-bloomberg-television-anchor-and-editor-large-francine-lacqua}}</ref> In each episode, Lacqua interviews prominent or senior business figures inside one of the passenger capsules of the [[London Eye]] [[Ferris wheel]] in [[London]].<ref name="s1">{{cite web|url=http://www.nfvzone.com/news/2011/03/31/5413811.htm|title=Bloomberg Television Debuts 'Eye To Eye'|publisher=NFV Zone|date=31 March 2011|accessdate=15 August 2015|archivedate=15 August 2015|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150815072624/http://www.nfvzone.com/news/2011/03/31/5413811.htm}}</ref>
The program is similar to another Bloomberg Television series ''[[High Flyers (TV series)|High Flyers]]'', which conducts interviews on the [[Singapore Flyer]].
==Broadcast== [[File:Francine Lacqua.jpg|thumb|right|Francine Lacqua, the host of ''Eye to Eye''.]] The series premiered on 28 March 2011 on Bloomberg Television's [[Europe, the Middle East and Africa]] feeds.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2011-03-28/bloomberg-television-goes-eye-to-eye-with-business-visionaries|title=Bloomberg Television Goes 'Eye To Eye' With Business Visionaries|date=29 March 2011|accessdate=15 August 2015|work=Bloomberg|subscription=yes}}</ref> The series premiered in [[Asia Pacific]] markets on 11 June 2011.<ref name="asia">{{cite web|url=http://www.onscreenasia.com/article/bloomberg-television-goes-eye-to-eye-with-business-visionaries/8536|title=Bloomberg Television goes ‘Eye to Eye’ with business visionaries|date=10 June 2011|work=On Screen Asia|accessdate=15 August 2015|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150815073221/http://www.onscreenasia.com/article/bloomberg-television-goes-eye-to-eye-with-business-visionaries/8536|archivedate=15 August 2015}}</ref>
