[[Image:Vattenfall office building 20060913 001.jpg|thumb|right|260px|Rusck was head of the [[Vattenfall]] company between 1948 and 1957]] '''John Åke J:son Rusck''' (9 August 1912 &ndash; 24 September 1978) was a [[Sweden|Swedish]] [[businessman]].
He was CEO of Sweden's major state [[hydro power]] company [[Vattenfall]] between 1948 and 1957 and then CEO of the [[SAS Group]] from 1958-1961.<ref>[http://runeberg.org/vemardet/1969/0832.html Åke Rusck in ''Vem är det'' 1969]</ref>
He was elected a member of the [[Royal Swedish Academy of Engineering Sciences]] in 1950.
